<section>
  <h1>Settings</h1>
  <p>This Gateway exposes only configuration via environment variables. Edit your `.env` and restart the service.</p>
  <ul>
    <li><code>RATE_LIMIT_SEND</code> (global throttler; login uses a fixed limit in code)</li>
    <li><code>MAX_TEXT_LENGTH</code></li>
    <li><code>WAHA_BASE_URL</code>, <code>WAHA_API_KEY</code></li>
    <li><code>API_TOKEN_PREFIX</code></li>
  </ul>
</section>
